{
  "stem": "7860.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course, I gave her a hard time now realizing as an old man.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she was crying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I'll never give you up because I love you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So she was very emotional.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She was sitting in the bushes and watching me, the performance I gave for these people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So she really loved me then.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then as soon as I learned how to walk and talk, I was going to cheder.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after cheder in the summertime we start playing with the children, other children, I was going around peddling-- my mother used to take my little brother, the youngest brother, Ruven, on her arm, and my middle brother, Abraham, by the arm, and walk with her suit, with her little baskets full of goodies, and try to peddle to the rich Jews in those [NON-ENGLISH], resorts.",
      "word_count": 66
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my father, he did the same thing selling this stuff to the rich Jews.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And how old I was, I do not remember.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I must have been-- today, psychology would say I was reacting, jealous of other children.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because other children had young fathers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father was 20 years older than my mother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was reacting also that other children had younger fathers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Other fathers used to go to the bakery for Passover and buy matzo.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My father sneak in through the bushes with a pillowcase full of matzo-- he was begging from house to house for we have more matzo for Passover.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I resented that-- why are other children better than I am?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why should my mother and father sneak in through the bushes?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I gave myself a promise.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
